    "This MODIFY-designed Rma cyt c library contained the top 1000 variants (Supplementary Data 1).",
    "The gene fragment library was synthesized using the oligo-pool technology 46 and cloned into a pET-22b(+) vector with an N-terminal pelB sequence (see Supplementary Information A.7 for details).",
